Econet_HardwareAddresses  (&40020) (3.50+)
#Parent Econet_
<=	R0 =	address of 68B54
 	R1 =	address of FIQ mask
 	R2 =	bit map to apply to FIQ mask

This SWI provides details of the hardware interface, for use with diagnostic tools only. An error is returned if the network is not using native Econet as the transport.
#Line
See <PRM 5a, page 276=>PRM-5a:276>.
